lmckenzi pushed 8 commits to branch Branch_R4B_Lloyd.

  • Fixed FHIR-19955 (bad schematrons) (76662b9)
  • FHIR-26307 - Fixed dom-3 schematron. (Fixed an issue with the expression while I was at it.) Note that the schematron isn't smart enough to only focus on uri/canonical/reference, so it'll be happy if it looks like anything is pointing to the contained resource or anything in contained is pointing to root. (e4eaafd)
  • FHIR-26565 - Handle Parameters being empty (72896d0)
  • https://jira.hl7.org/browse/FHIR-21180 - Fixed Parameters schematron (b7b9512)
  • https://jira.hl7.org/browse/FHIR-29595 - corrected case on 'boolean' in que-7 (94f776f)
  • https://jira.hl7.org/browse/FHIR-29595 - corrected context invariant (ccf1dab)
  • https://jira.hl7.org/browse/FHIR-26306 (2a2076d)
  • More on https://jira.hl7.org/browse/FHIR-26306 (ae04ec9)
